fields.physical_description:
1. pond; rectangular with a raised edge with sloping sides; painted green with orange, yellow, red, blue and white. In the centre is a raised knob with a hole in the top. Underside painted beige. 5¼in x 3½in x ¾in (13.4x8.9x1.9cm)
2. statue; painted cream; raised right arm; knob at bottom which fits into the hole in the centre of the pond. Ht. ¾in (1.9cm)
3. lily pad; round based with three leaves; painted dark green with cream
and yellow flower. gt. diam 7/8in (2.2cm)
4,5. corner rockery blocks; painted beige with green, white, blue, red and yellow. 1¾in x 1¾in x ht. 1 1/8in (4.4x4.4x2.8cm)
6. rockery part; painted beige with blue, orange, red, white and green. 
     1¾in x 1¾in x 1 1/8in (4.4x4.4x2.8cm)
7,8. stone wall; shaped as layers and painted beige. 3½in x 5/8in (8.9x1.6cm)
9,10. stone corner pillars; shaped as layers and painted beige. 
          7/8in x 7/8in x ¾in (2.2x2.2x1.9cm)
11,12. lattice fencing; lower 'woven' part painted dark brown; upper open part painted green; one stabilising foot. 3½in x 2 3/8in (8.9x6cm)
13-32. crazy paving; painted beige, marked on the underside MADE IN ENGLAND BY BRITAINS LTD 7/8in sq. (2.2cm)
33. flower bed square; painted dark brown, marked on the underside MADE IN ENGLAND BY BRITAINS LTD LONDON NO. 066  2 5/8in sq. (6.7cm)
34. flower bed corner; painted dark brown with green on two sides, marked on underside MADE IN ENGLAND BY BRITAINS LTD NO. 05 
      1¾in sq. (4.4cm)
35,36. flower bed corner; painted dark brown with one corner green, marked on underside MADE IN ENGLAND BY BRITAINS LTD LONDON NO. 03  1¾in sq. (4.4cm)
37. flower bed edging; painted dark brown with green along one side, marked on underside MADE IN ENGLAND BY BRITAINS LTD LONDON NO. 01.  3½in x 1¾in (8.9x4.4cm)
38-42. lawn; thin squares of cork painted green. 1¾in sq.  (4.4cm)
43. hedge; loofah painted green; yellow and red; glued to a thin strip of wood. L. 7¾in (19.7cm)
44-46. fencing; wooden slats painted white/cream with a green base. 
            7 7/8in x 1 5/8in x 5/8in (20x4.1x1.6cm)
47. fencing with a central swing gate; painted white/cream with a green base. 7 7/8in x 1 5/8in x 5/8in  (20x4.1x1.6cm)
48. well; round base with pitched roof; cast lead painted red; green and cream with the remains of thread round the axis of the handle. 
      Ht. 3in x diam 1¾in  (7.6x4.4cm)
49. bucket for the well; handle missing; plain lead; ht. ½in (1.3cm)
50. dog kennel; painted green, marked MADE IN ENGLAND. 1¾in x 
       1 1/8in x 1 5/8in  (4.4x2.8x4.1cm)
51. flower pot; turned wood painted red; with a hole in the top. 
       ¾in x diam 7/8in (1.9x2.2cm)
52. garden gnome which is actually a dwarf from the Snow White and Seven Dwarfs set; painted red and yellow with a white beard. 
       Ht. 1¾in (4.4cm)
53,54. flower bunch; painted white on green 
55-58. flower bunch; painted blue on green 
59. bush; with purple flowers 
60. bush; with white flowers 
61. bush; with yellow flowers
62,63. small flowers; painted red; one has two the other 3 flowers 
64. small flower; painted pink on green 
65. small flower; painted yellow on green; two flowers 

66. small flower; painted yellow on green; three flowers 
67. small flower; painted yellow on green; four flowers 
68. small flower; painted white on green; two flowers 
69,70. small flower; painted white on green; three flowers 
71,72; small flower; painted orange on green; three flowers 
73-75. row of flowers; painted white on green; two flowers 
76. row of flowers; painted yellow on green; two flowers 
77. row of flowers; painted blue on green; two flowers 
78. row of flowers; painted blue on green; three flowers 
79,80. row of flowers; painted white on green; three flowers 
81-83. row of flowers; painted yellow on green; three flowers
84,85. tulip; one flower painted white on green 
86. tulip; one flower painted pink on green 
87. tulip; one flower painted red on green 
88. tulip; two flowers painted white on green 
89. tulip; two flowers painted orange on green 
90. sprig; two flowers painted pink on green
